context:
KR:
<i>&lt;color=#5bffde&gt;뜰 앞에서 서러워하는 꽃장례 지내는 사람이여</i>&lt;/color&gt;
EN:
<i>&lt;color=#5bffde&gt;O the garden's sorrow-bearer, lamenter at the flower-funeral</i>&lt;/color&gt;

KR:
<i>&lt;color=#5bffde&gt;꽃갈퀴 홀로 들고 눈물을 짓더니</i>&lt;/color&gt;
EN:
<i>&lt;color=#5bffde&gt;Flower-rake in hand, teardrops in eyes,</i>&lt;/color&gt;

KR:
<i>&lt;color=#5bffde&gt;빈 가지 뿌려진 눈물엔 핏자국이 어려 있네</i>&lt;/color&gt;
EN:
<i>&lt;color=#5bffde&gt;You carve bloodstained tears upon branches floral.</i>&lt;/color&gt;

KR:
<i>&lt;color=#5bffde&gt;어젯밤 뜰 밖에서 슬픈 노래가 들렸는데</i>&lt;/color&gt;
EN:
<i>&lt;color=#5bffde&gt;I heard yesternight from the garden a song of grief,</i>&lt;/color&gt;

KR:
<i>&lt;color=#5bffde&gt;그것은 꽃 넋과 가는 새 넋의 울음이었지</i>&lt;/color&gt;
EN:
<i>&lt;color=#5bffde&gt;An elegy for a flower and a bird departing.</i>&lt;/color&gt;

KR:
<i>&lt;color=#5bffde&gt;가는 봄이 안타까워도 할 수 있는 것은 없으니</i>&lt;/color&gt;
EN:
<i>&lt;color=#5bffde&gt;Availed naught to hold the parting spring,</i>&lt;/color&gt;

KR:
<i>&lt;color=#5bffde&gt;그 수많은 울음소리를 그저 듣기만 하는 수밖에</i>&lt;/color&gt;
EN:
<i>&lt;color=#5bffde&gt;Surrendered I become, heeding the endless woe sans relief.</i>&lt;/color&gt;

KR:
&lt;color=#9a2d30&gt;이제 알겠느냐, 너는 할 수 있는 게 무엇도 없단다.&lt;/color&gt;
EN:
&lt;color=#9a2d30&gt;Do you understand now, child? There is nothing you can do.&lt;/color&gt;

KR:
&lt;color=#9a2d30&gt;그러니… &lt;/color&gt;
EN:
&lt;color=#9a2d30&gt;Thus...&lt;/color&gt;

KR:
&lt;너도 보았던 거지…? 그 모든 광경을.&gt;
EN:
&lt;... you saw everything that happened here, didn't you? All of it.&gt;
